title: Record whisky fetches $1.2 mln ini Dubai
text:
Record whisky fetches $1.2 mln ini Dubai 2:16pm BST - 01:54
The world's most expensive bottles of whisky have been sold in Dubai. The two limited editions of Macallan Scotch were bought for $600,000 each, thought to be the most paid by a private buyer. Nawied Jabarkhyl reports
